# Stack (Timeless Electronix)

## Architecture

- **Monorepo** with `client/` (React SPA) and `server/` (Express API).
- Client talks to server via `/api/*` (Vite proxy in dev, reverse proxy in prod).

## Client (`client/`)

- React 18 + TypeScript + Vite + TailwindCSS v4 + React Router.
- State: `QuoteContext` (localStorage-backed cart) for quote items.
- API calls: `src/lib/api.ts` (public), `src/lib/adminApi.ts` (admin with JWT).
- Types: `src/lib/types.ts` — all shared interfaces.
- Pages: `src/pages/` — flat for public, `admin/` subfolder for admin.
- Components: `src/components/` — shared UI (Header, Footer, ProductCard).

## Server (`server/`)

- Express + TypeScript, run with `tsx` in dev.
- Mongoose ODM for MongoDB. Models in `src/models/`.
- Zod for request validation in routes.
- JWT auth for admin routes (`ADMIN_SECRET` env var for login, `JWT_SECRET` for tokens).
- Cloudinary SDK for image uploads. Resend for transactional email.
- Routes: `src/routes/` — `products`, `contact`, `quotes`, `admin`.

## Conventions

- Use `async/await` with try/catch, pass errors to Express `next()`.
- Validate request bodies with Zod schemas in route handlers.
- Use `.lean()` on Mongoose queries when the document won't be modified.
- TailwindCSS classes only — no CSS modules, no styled-components.
- Custom colors defined in `client/src/index.css` under `@theme`: `bg-primary`, `bg-secondary`, `bg-card`, `green-brand`, `green-accent`, `text-primary`, `text-secondary`, `border`.

## Environment

- All env vars documented in `.env.example`. Server reads them via Zod-validated `src/config/env.ts`.
- Optional services (Cloudinary, Resend) degrade gracefully when keys are empty.
